ded lazyload" typeof="foaf:Image" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/Untitled design - 2021-06-26T112806.872.png?itok=CQPzASji" alt=""><img class="media-element file-embedded lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/Untitled design - 2021-06-26T112806.872.png?itok=CQPzASji" alt data-lazy-src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/Untitled%20design%20-%202021-06-26T112806.872.png?itok=CQPzASji&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img class="media-element file-embedded lazyload" typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/Untitled design - 2021-06-26T112806.872.png?itok=CQPzASji" alt="">   The low-key marriage was solemnised at the Sheikh Sharif Ibrahim Saleh’s mosque in Maiduguri on Friday.  <img class="media-element file-embedded lazyload" typeof="foaf:Image" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/WhatsApp Image 2021-06-26 at 11.10.20 AM (4).jpeg?itok=7q2RaLcp" alt=""><img class="media-element file-embedded lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/WhatsApp Image 2021-06-26 at 11.10.20 AM (4).jpeg?itok=7q2RaLcp" alt data-lazy-src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/WhatsApp%20Image%202021-06-26%20at%2011.10.20%20AM%20(4).jpeg?itok=7q2RaLcp&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img class="media-element file-embedded lazyload" typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/WhatsApp Image 2021-06-26 at 11.10.20 AM (4).jpeg?itok=7q2RaLcp" alt=""> Zainab Algoni Abdulwahid   SaharaReporters gathered that the event was performed secretly to avoid public criticism while Zainab is expected to relocate to Abuja on Sunday.  <img class="media-element file-embedded lazyload" typeof="foaf:Image" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/WhatsApp Image 2021-06-26 at 11.10.20 AM (3).jpeg?itok=YJ9r2p67" alt=""><img class="media-element file-embedded lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/WhatsApp Image 2021-06-26 at 11.10.20 AM (3).jpeg?itok=YJ9r2p67" alt data-lazy-src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/WhatsApp%20Image%202021-06-26%20at%2011.10.20%20AM%20(3).jpeg?itok=YJ9r2p67&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img class="media-element file-embedded lazyload" typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://saharareporters.com/sites/default/files/styles/normal_medium/public/WhatsApp Image 2021-06-26 at 11.10.20 AM (3).jpeg?itok=YJ9r2p67" alt="">   A mini party was also held at the bride’s family residence in Gwange 1 Ward, Malut Shuwa Street, Maiduguri. “The Senate President of Nigeria, Lawan, got married to a young Shuwa Arab Girl at Maiduguri. Her name is Zainab Algoni Abdulwahid. “They got hooked after Jumu’at Prayer on Friday in Maiduguri. The bride will travel to Abuja on Sunday. “The ceremony was done secretly. The Senate President didn’t attend the Nikaah, but he sent a delegation to go and get it done. “But the bride did her ceremony at their house in Gwange 1 Ward, Malut Shuwa Street, Maiduguri,” a source told SaharaReporters. When contacted, Ola Awoniyi, Special Adviser on Media to the Senate President, said he was at the airport. A text message sent to him was also not replied to. Politics  Exclusive News Reports   AddThis :  Original Author : SaharaReporters, New York  Disable advertisements :